● AI Features - Detailed Descriptions

 

  ---
  AI Geographic Insights (Customers tab)
  - Analyzes your own sales data by region
  - Answers: "Where are WE selling well/poorly?"
  - Based on actual revenue, customer counts, growth rates from your data
  - Internal focus - your performance across markets
  - Example insight: "Your Texas region grew 23% YoY and has your highest revenue per customer"

 

  ---
  AI Market Overview (dedicated tab)
  - Researches external market context via web search
  - Answers: "What's happening in the market around us?"
  - Industry trends, competitive landscape, regional market dynamics
  - External focus - the broader market environment
  - Example insight: "The California nursery market is experiencing consolidation with 3 major acquisitions in 2025"

 

  ---
  AI Customer Intelligence (AI Customer Insight tab)
  - Researches individual customers via web search
  - Answers: "Who is this customer and what's their potential?"
  - Business profile, market segment, strategic fit assessment
  - Customer-specific focus - deep dive on one account
  - Example insight: "ABC Landscaping is a commercial contractor expanding into municipal projects - opportunity to cross-sell larger container sizes"

 

  ---
  Ask AI (dedicated tab)
  - Queries your dashboard data using natural language
  - Answers: "What does our data say about X?"
  - Instant analysis of sales, customers, items, trends
  - Data exploration focus - freeform questions about your metrics
  - Example insight: "Your top 5 customers represent 34% of YTD revenue, with 3 of them showing declining orders vs last year"

● FULFILL™ Intelligence Dashboard - Feature Summary

 

  Tabs & Navigation

 

  - 10 Dashboard Tabs covering all aspects of business performance
  - 3 AI-powered tabs (AI Market Overview, AI Customer Insight, Ask AI)
  - 7 Core analytics tabs (Executive Summary, Trends, Customers, Items, Products, Sizes, Sales Team, Inventory)

 

  Charts & Visualizations

 

  - 40+ interactive charts including:
    - Line charts (trends, moving averages, YoY comparisons)
    - Bar charts (top performers, period comparisons)
    - Pie charts (revenue distribution, segmentation)
    - Waterfall charts (revenue bridge analysis)
    - Histograms (order size distribution)
    - Combo charts (dual-axis visualizations)

 

  KPI Metrics

 

  - 60+ business metrics tracked including:
    - YTD Sales, Orders, Units, Customers
    - Average Order Size, Selling Price, Revenue/Customer
    - YoY change percentages across all dimensions
    - Customer health indicators (new, growing, stable, declining, lost)
    - Revenue concentration by tier (A/B/C)

 

  Data Tables

 

  - 15+ sortable/filterable tables with:
    - Conditional formatting (green/red for performance)
    - Pagination and sorting
    - Tier analysis (80/20 Pareto)
    - Top gainers/decliners rankings

 

  AI Features (4 Total)

 

  - Natural Language Query (Ask AI tab) - Ask questions about your data in plain English
  - AI Customer Intelligence (AI Customer Insight tab) - Deep research on individual customers with web search
  - AI Market Overview (AI Market Overview tab) - Regional market analysis and competitive insights
  - AI Geographic Insights (Customers tab) - Regional market context, growth opportunities, and competitive positioning based on your geographic sales data

 

  Advanced Analytics

 

  - Year-over-Year Analysis - TY vs LY across all dimensions
  - Revenue Bridge (Waterfall) - Track new, lost, growing, declining
  - 80/20 Pareto Analysis - Identify top revenue drivers
  - Customer Segmentation - Tier classification and movement tracking
  - Geographic Analysis - Regional performance by market area
  - Fulfillment Analysis - Track lost opportunity by size

Development Workflow

  • Submitting PRs and what to expect in review

Patterns & Components

  • What Gabby looks for in PR reviews (patterns, component reuse)

First Task
